Overcrowding creatures threaten Arcanum Outpost. Thin their numbers to keep the people safe.

Kill {@LinkCreature:54#250#baelith arachnens}, {@LinkCreature:54#240#spineback noruks}, and {@LinkCreature:54#160#rippertusk sabertooths}.

Report to Lashada back at the outpost when mission is complete.
You've earned the thanks of the federation!
